Package: debian-nvidia-installer
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dialog, findutils, gawk, mokutil, pciutils, wget
Description: NVIDIA driver installer with a Bash TUI
 This tool allows you to install NVIDIA drivers on Debian using an interactive
 text-based interface (TUI). It automates steps such as package installation,
 compatibility checks, and graphics environment configuration.